 <text>
  <front>
   <head>ELEGY. TO ALMERIA.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">HAIL, blissful scenes of early youth,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">So sacred once to love and truth,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">When my Almeria, matchless maid,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">With angel charms, adorn'd the shade;</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Regardless of each fond delight,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Though time pursu'd his steady flight;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Yet, as he flew, around his wing</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Gay pleasure twin'd the wreath of spring,</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Whilst Hope, fair daughter of the sky,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">With golden tress and azure eye,</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Benignant turn'd her gladd'ning lyre,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And bade my soul to bliss aspire;</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But now no more along these plains</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">She pours her sweet seraphic strains;</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No more Almeria wanders near;</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">In vain, alas! I seek her here:</l>
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Yet, as by fond remembrance led,</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">My fav'rite scenes I pensive tread;</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">There peaceful shades, yon conscious grove,</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Restore awhile the joys of love.</l>
     <l n="21" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Recalling thus the blissful past,</l>
     <l n="22" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">For ever sweet delusion last:</l>
     <l n="23" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Nor let Oblivion's gloomy veil</l>
     <l n="24" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">From Mem'ry shroud the tender tale.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
